TASK_DESCRIPTION=Build the /doey-masterplan skill — Doey's crown jewel planning system. Spawns 10 agents doing ultrathink deep research, asks hard questions about intentionality, produces vertical-phase plans with test gates between each phase. Three pillars: Truth (understand what really matters), Taste (simple, useful, beautifully done), Intentionality (the binding concept — every decision traces to clear intent). Design doc at /tmp/doey/doey/masterplan-skill-design.md.
TASK_SUBTASKS=1:Phase 0: Intent Interrogation module — ultrathink agent that challenges assumptions before any planning:done\n2:Phase 1: Multi-Agent Research Swarm — 10 parallel ultrathink agents each with a distinct research angle:done\n3:Phase 2: Synthesis module — merge 10 reports, resolve contradictions, produce unified understanding:done\n4:Phase 3: Vertical Phase Designer — each phase independently deployable, testable, valuable; test gates between phases:done\n5:Phase 4: Plan Presentation — beautiful AskUserQuestion flow for approval/modification:done\n6:Phase 5: Task Generation — convert approved phases into linked Doey tasks with verification subtasks:done\n7:Write SKILL.md with YAML frontmatter, trigger pattern, and full orchestration logic:done\n8:Dispatched to W3 Subtaskmaster (4 workers):done\n9:W3.1: Research existing skill patterns (planned-task structure, frontmatter, triggers):done\n10:W3.2: Create SKILL.md.tmpl scaffold + Phase 0 (Intent Interrogation):done\n11:W3.3: Write Phase 1 (Multi-Agent Research Swarm — 10 ultrathink agents):done\n12:W3.4: Shared utility sections — plan ID, directory setup, output format:done\n13:W3.1: Write Phases 4-5 (Presentation + Task Generation):done\n14:W3.2: Assemble complete SKILL.md.tmpl from all sections:done
